mal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，初步plan咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上次去Melbourne同Sydney半個幾月都未玩夠 你8日去咁多地方為左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為Sydney好似玩唔到8日，所以諗住飛去其它城市"},{"pid":"72935aa79f2c5c06287303945b9e087448e49092","tid":296483,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪想打卡炸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，初步plan咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上次去Melbourne同Sydney半個幾月都未玩夠 你8日去咁多地方為左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講晒la,長有長玩，短有短玩，洗唔洗一個地方預一年呀<br />\n<br />\n如果正係Sydney 其實兩日夠，海灘睇你去唔去"},{"pid":"d67512a39608e1e0d9b9eb26dc0e20b6a01d321e","tid":296483,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"藍山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ae55f6353820f98e890aa5f250d276565ed0de","tid":296483,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n藍山其實唔差，去開去埋都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔真係好正"},{"pid":"defb77b7fb8baa4384f8cbc25fa3091c645ad584","tid":296483,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:27:28.000Z","msg":"黃金海岸番悉尼果班機可以最尾個日先搭，但黃金海岸值唔值去兩日?冬天我唔會玩水上活動"},{"pid":"8621a984a0bac0d1c3b5b28ca6b7de939ea7cb92","tid":296483,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:28:26.000Z","msg":"如果唔去坎培拉有乜好介紹?"},{"pid":"439c882adf4eea2eb79338055b7c3719c7b821cf","tid":296483,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痴線, 趕到咁, 唔駛訓?</blockquote><br />\n邊日行程趕?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成個trip 都趕啦<br />\n基本上得一日係悉尼市區<br />\n雖然悉尼市區係冇咩野睇<br />\n但去下fish market, 搭下船睇harbour bridge 同opera house<br />\n都已經一日<br />\n<br />\nday3 去布里斯本得半日,<br />\n你又唔知做咩, 不如直接飛黃金海岸玩足3日好過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議你一日唔好排咁多行程<br />\n澳洲生活節奏好慢, 你出去食飯叫賣單都可能要等5分鐘<br />\n如果你唔揸車, d 時間仲唔見駛"},{"pid":"9ace4c456aa94edc7f1b65321d829c0d6ef3bb5b","tid":296483,"uid":51470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪想打卡炸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，初步plan咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上次去Melbourne同Sydney半個幾月都未玩夠 你8日去咁多地方為左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我黎緊都plan左去MEL SYD 兩個星期左右 除左大路野 有咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3655a76085535a96ccbd06c33f0dbae6427920b","tid":296483,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痴線, 趕到咁, 唔駛訓?</blockquote><br />\n邊日行程趕?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成個trip 都趕啦<br />\n基本上得一日係悉尼市區<br />\n雖然悉尼市區係冇咩野睇<br />\n但去下fish market, 搭下船睇harbour bridge 同opera house<br />\n都已經一日<br />\n<br />\nday3 去布里斯本得半日,<br />\n你又唔知做咩, 不如直接飛黃金海岸玩足3日好過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議你一日唔好排咁多行程<br />\n澳洲生活節奏好慢, 你出去食飯叫賣單都可能要等5分鐘<br />\n如果你唔揸車, d 時間仲唔見駛</blockquote><br />\nday 1 同 day 7會係悉尼玩<br />\nday 1係早機到而day 7係晚機走<br />\n所以悉尼會玩到一日半<br />\n布里斯本同埋坎培拉係後尾加上去"},{"pid":"f905ecabbaeca27c38d88502ebd9b8ad164c37da","tid":296483,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟將會8月去澳洲<br />\nDay 1: 朝早落機